$ Avaloq desks

So called *desks* allow to run and view reports based on modifiable criteria (such as business partner or name of container).

A prominent desk is the *portfolio desk* (PFM desk).

Others are the *central services desk* (used for administration, monitoring, logging, background processes (→ Companies-Products/Avaloq/BGP[BGPs]?) etc.

The *customisation desk* is used to customise Avaloq Core (see → Companies-Products/Avaloq/development/sources[sources]).
-
The *parametrisation desk* displays and administers sources.

